    {
      "instruction": "<p>Put your <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> in the oven for 2-3 min or until warmed through</p><p>Add the <strong>shredded lettuce</strong> and <strong>diced tomato</strong> to the<strong> dressing</strong> and mix it all together – this is your <strong>zesty salad</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>warmed ciabatta[s]</strong> in half</p>",
