    {
      "instruction": "<p>Fill the <strong>ciabatta </strong>with the <strong>Mexican-style chilli chicken</strong>,<strong> </strong>a dollop of your <strong>mayo</strong>, the <strong>sliced tomato </strong>and a <strong>lettuce leaf </strong>– this is your <strong>Mexican-style chilli chicken torta</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>paprika fries</strong> and <strong>zesty salad</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
